<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>${title}</title>
	<!--
    	compile the css via lessjs - dev-mode
    -->
    	<link href="resources/theme/less/main.less" rel="stylesheet/less" type="text/css" />
    <!--
    	include responsive.less if you want to use the responsive-features - dev-mode
    	<link href="resources/theme/less/responsive.less" rel="stylesheet/less" type="text/css" />	
    -->
    <!-- 
		hint: in production include the the compiled css
    	<link href="resources/theme/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    	and if you like:
    	<link href="resources/theme/css/responsive.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    -->
    
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    	<script src="resources/theme/js/html5shiv.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>
<body>

	<div class="navbar navbar-fixed-top">
		<div class="navbar-inner">
			<div class="container">
				<a class="brand" href="#">${title}</a>
			</div>
		</div>
    </div>

	<div class="container">
   
		<div class="hero-unit">
			<h1>${title}-Theme</h1>
			<p class="lead">${description}</p>
		</div>
      
		<h2>What's next?</h2>
      
		<ul>
			<li>Build your HTML and customize the less-files in resources/theme/less</li>
			<li>Don't touch the files in resources/theme/less/bootstrap! They will be overwritten on the next update</li>
			<li>Include resources/theme/less/responsive.less if you want to use the Bootstrap responsive features</li>
			<li>For development the less files are compiled by <a href="http://www.lesscss.de/">less.js</a></li>
			<li>Once you've finished just build the war with maven. The less files will be compiled with the <a href="https://github.com/marceloverdijk/lesscss-maven-plugin">lesscss-maven-plugin</a></li>
			<li>Include the war in your application as a <a href="http://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-war-plugin/overlays.html">war overlay</a></li>
			<li>Want to update bootstrap? Just use boottheme update</li>
		</ul>
	      
		<hr />
	      
		<footer>
			<p>Version: ${version}</p>
		</footer>
      
    </div>
	
    <script src="resources/theme/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <!-- you won't need the less.min.js in production -->
    <script src="resources/theme/js/less.min.js"></script>
    <script src="resources/theme/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>	